summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from Rufus Smith and Charlotte B. Smith, his wife, to the City of Seattle, executed on the 7th day of February, 1925; and from Sarah L. Edmunds and Frederick J. Edmunds, her husband, to the City of Seattle, executed on the 30th day of March, 1925, for easements for a sewer over and across portions of Tracts 52 and 53 respectively, Lincoln Park.
